==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stevedore
<hw>Ste"ve*dore`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.
<ets>estivador</ets> a packer, a stower, fr. <ets>estivar</ets> to pack,
to stow, L. <ets>stipare</ets> to press, compress, probably akin to E.
<ets>stiff</ets>. See <er>Stiff</er>, <er>Stive</er> to stuff.]</ety>
<def>One whose occupation is to load and unload vessels in port; one who
stows a cargo in a hold.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Steven</ent>⟦br⟧
